videos.description: Illinois State alum Doug Collins has a few words for the No. 1 ranked Wildcats before Redbirds visit Lexington.
videos.headline: Doug Collins has a message for Kentucky

videos.description: Illinois State's Devaughn Akoon-Purcell skies in for the putback slam that puts the Redbirds up 6 early against Kentucky.

videos.description: In the final seconds of the first half, Illinois State's DeVaughn Akoon-Purcell drives the lane and scores on an up-and-under layup to tie the game with Kentucky at 31.
videos.headline: Smooth up-and-under ties the game for Illinois State

videos.description: Kentucky's Isaiah Briscoe drives to the lane, catches the inbounds pass and score a layup to give the Wildcats a seven point lead over Illinois State.
videos.headline: Isaiah Briscoe scores off inbounds pass

videos.description: Kentucky's Alex Poythress gets the offensive rebound and scores his own bucket while drawing a foul against Illinois State.
videos.headline: Poythress cleans up the glass

videos.headline: Marcus Lee's performance key in Wildcats win
